data.description: Better than new! This house is less than a year old and fully established! The location is fantastic! You have the best view in Anthology, centered on the park! And just a short drive to I-25 and less than 10 minutes to Parker Mainstreet. 4 bedrooms (one located on the main), 3 baths, a dedicated office and a loft. Upgraded, light and bright modern finishes throughout the entire house. Stainless steel appliances, Smart fridge, Smart washer and dryer, Radon mitigation system, Hardwired security system, Century home connect smart home upgrade, Prewired for audio in 4 zones (primary bedroom, loft, living room and patio), Gas line to BBQ. Full unfinished basement, 2 car garage. Driveway faces SE, so snow melts quickly! Community pool and clubhouse. Come enjoy this beautiful, new home that's ready for you now! Homeowner is a licensed realtor.
